HEADWORD: Xiphidium
<hw>Xi*phid"i*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
from Gr. <?/, dim. of <grk>xi`fos</grk> sword.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
